name: Real Racing CSR Car Parking Job
name_original: Real Racing CSR Car Parking Job
description:
Real Racing CSR Car Parking Job

This game is designed to get you’re parking skills up, and to show every driving school instructor you know how to park your car safely in different challenging parking situations.

This 3D parking game takes place in several different setting, set in a cool looking 3D-Style.

This game is the most beautiful and most interesting game where you have to city car parking. You get in the car, and to go to the destination. You put it perfectly into the parking lot, to validate and move to the next level.

To complete levels, you must pass all the checkpoints and stop into the parking spot. In some levels there are reverse parking spots.

Key features:

=> Realistic Sounds
=> Best Real Crashes
=> Lots of Challenges to Complete
=> Addictive game play
=> Tap on right to take your shift reverse gear
